data-triple-N3.o: "The California Institute of Technology (commonly referred to as Caltech) is a private research university located in Pasadena, California, United States. Caltech has six academic divisions with strong emphases on science and engineering. Its 124-acre primary campus is located approximately 11 mi northeast of downtown Los Angeles.
